Real Madrid have lost their last 5 UCL games (PSG, Ajax, CSKA, CSKA, Juventus) without Sergio Ramos. [<br />
@pedritonumeros<br />
]

James Rodriguez: &ldquo;I feel the love of the Real Madrid fans and it fills me with happiness.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
James Rodriguez: &ldquo;We always believe in our work and in the coach. We have to think about the next game now. We are Real Madrid and we have to think about what is to come.&rdquo;

Vicente del Bosque refuses to comment on Real Madrid's recent problems:<br />
<br />
&quot;I neither owe nor wish that my statements bother Real Madrid.&quot;

Zidane: &ldquo;Do the Mourinho rumors bother me? This is difficult but it is the reality. I am interested in what we are going to do as a team.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Zidane: &quot;Eriksen or Van de Beek? It's a club thing. This is the squad. We are who we are here&quot;

Former French player and coach Rolland Courbis: &ldquo;Hazard was seen as the locomotive in terms of signings, but in reality he's the rear end of a train. He arrived 6 or 7 kilograms overweight, it's rude. If we keep saying he's lazy, this player should never signed for Real Madrid.&quot;<br />
<br />
Former French player and coach Rolland Courbis: &ldquo;You have to look at what happened when Zidane left in 2018. He didn't dare resolve the problem that he had when it came to changing four or five players in a team that had won the Champions League three times.&rdquo;

🎙️Ramos : &quot;Although it was not a good season, it is a good sign that there are Madrid players in the XI.&quot;<br />
<br />
🎙️Ramos [Criticism about Marcelo]: &ldquo;He is one of the best in the world. Everyone is free to comment ... it is difficult to please everyone.&quot;

Zidane: &quot;I&rsquo;m annoyed with the injuries but not worried. This is part of football that can't be controlled. The people who work at Real Madrid are very good. There are other factors, many games, little rest.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Zidane &quot;Crisis? It&rsquo;s always like that, we only concentrate and worry about the next game. Forget about Sevilla and think about tomorrow, play with the same attitude.&rdquo;

Guti: &ldquo;Nobody's going to do what Zidane has done as a coach at Real Madrid. It's always hard to return to a team and, little by little, they're improving.&quot;<br />
<br />
Guti: &ldquo;Is my dream to coach Real Madrid? No. My dream is to be a coach, that's all. Real Madrid is separate. When I speak of Real Madrid, I speak as a fan. I dream of being a coach, that's it.&quot;

Raul on Rodrygo: &ldquo;He motivates himself. From the beginning, the situation with him has been clear: he is a first-team player but when he can help Castilla, or Castilla can help him, he will come and play.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Raul: &ldquo;Rodrygo has played at a high level and has sacrificed himself, like all of his teammates. On Friday he was training with us, and although we don't know each other that well, every time that he comes and trains with Castilla, he gives his all &amp; everyone sees his potential.&rdquo;

Eden Hazard 🎙: &ldquo;I'm not a Galactico yet, I have to prove it. We all know the past of the number 7 on this team. I have to be the one to prove that I can be the best in the world. I don't doubt my abilities or my technique.&quot;<br />
<br />
Eden Hazard 🎙: &ldquo;I know they expect me to score 3 goals per game. You have to be patient.&rdquo;
